::Feline::

She jumped up and wakled quickly to HotRod. "Hold on there.  I don't 
need you getting any more damage than you already have."  She went up 
to HotRod and put his arm over her shoulder to help brace him.  She 
tried to take over to the lab table and have him lay down.  "If 
you'll be patient, I'll have you fixed up in a few cycles."  She 
looked over at K-9.  "Help me with him, he's heavy."
